@@gBRAWLER@@W

Brawlers are ruthless close-range enforcers who overwhelm opponents through
repetition, pressure, and punishing body mechanics.

@@gPassive class advantages@@W
  * @@wBare-hand direct-hit damage@@W bonus (+0.75% per level, up to +75% at 100).
  * @@wCombo-family strike damage@@W bonus on remort/adept combo attacks
    (+1.5% per level, up to +150% at 100).
  * @@wMartial strike damage@@W bonus for palmstrike/pummel/aurabolt family
    (+0.375% per level, up to +37.5% at 100).

@@gUnique Brawler mechanics@@W
  * Access to @@wBrawler stance@@W.
  * Excellent bridge between combo pressure and unarmed sustained damage.
  * Uses @@wConstitution@@W as prime remort attribute.

@@gBrawler reincarnation bonuses@@W
  * @@wBrawler + Monk remort reincarnations >= 20@@W unlocks
    @@wEquip Fist@@W and @@wDual Fist@@W permanently.

